CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: WF International is principally engaged in the provision of supply, installation, fitting-out and/or maintenance services for HVAC systems and floor heating systems. Our current primary focus is on collaborating with property development companies that offer high-end fully furnished homes. We provide these clients with comprehensive electromechanical solutions for HVAC systems and floor heating systems. This approach has positioned us as an integrated supplier of both electromechanical products and installation services.
